<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[باب الأفعال الرافعة الاسم الناصبة الخبر]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c1">"ص"</span>:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>كان بها المبتدأ ارفع ناصبًا ... خبره كـ<span class="c1">"كان زيد صاحبا"</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>ومثل <span class="c1">"كان"</span>: <span class="c1">"ظل"</span> <span class="c1">"بات"</span> <span class="c1">"أضحى"</span> ... <span class="c1">"أصبح"</span> <span class="c1">"أمسى"</span> <span class="c1">"صار بشر سمحًا"</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>هكذا <span class="c1">"ليس"</span> و<span class="c1">"زال"</span> و<span class="c1">"برح"</span> ... <span class="c1">"فتئ"</span> و<span class="c1">"انفك"</span> وكل متضح<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وألزم الأربعة الأواخرا ... نفيًا كـ<span class="c1">"ما زال ابن عوف شاكِرا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ومثل "كان<span class="c1">": "</span>دام" بعد ما لدى ... إفهام مدة كقول من شَدَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>